== Carrot cake ==
Carrot cake ke borotho (Kuku) ke motswako wa di-carrot le metsi abo a fuduiwa. Motswako o o a apeiwa o bo o siliga mo pitseng gore o nne boleta, fa kuku yone e na le boleta jwa yone fa o e tshwara ka diatla.</br>
==Kapei le Metswako e e tsenngwang==
Fa go apewa carrot cake, go salwa morago ditaelo tsa go apaya borotho, [[Sukiri]] le [[mae]] dia kopanngwa mme morago go fuduiwe.</br>

Bontsi jwa metswako ya carrot cake e na le di ingredients tse di tshwanang le [[cinnamon]], [[manoko]],[[Paene-apole]] kana [[moretlwa wa sekgoa]]. Go nala lemon juice e e tsenngwang le icing sugar mo motswakong.

